Package mjerez.jmicrobench

Contains all the classes required to run the benchmarks.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
JMicrobench Implements this interface to run benchmarks.
 

Class Summary
BenchmarkRunner Base class which runs the Benchmarks.
HighChart Partial implementation in Java of the HighCharts JavaScript object.
PhasesProfiler This Class groups the TimeProfiler by phases of the benchmark.
Registry This Class acts as a central Registry of all TimeProfiler generated during the benchmarks.
TimeElement This Class corresponds to each portion of code measured.
TimeProfiler Base class used to do time profiling.
 

Enum Summary
BenchmarkRunner.Phase The possible phases of the benchmark: stopped, loading, warmup and profiling.
HighChart.ChartType The type of chart: Columns or Bars.
 

Package mjerez.jmicrobench Description

Contains all the classes required to run the benchmarks.
